  "caption": "A chill, lo-fi hip-hop track built on a foundation of warm, jazzy electric piano chords and a subtle vinyl crackle texture. The song opens with a spoken word intro before settling into a relaxed boom-bap drum groove and a smooth, understated bassline. A male rapper delivers conversational verses with a laid-back flow, while an airy, reverb-laden female vocal sings the melodic and emotional chorus. The arrangement remains consistent, focusing on the interplay between the grounded rap and the floating melody, concluding with a reflective spoken word outro as the instrumental fades.",
